Detailed Description

Receive free descriptor queue threshold information.

This structure contains information describing a receive free descriptor queue threshold.

Field Documentation

uint32_t CSL_UdmapRxFdqThresh::fEnable

[IN] If set, this threshold will be included in SOP FDQ selection

uint32_t CSL_UdmapRxFdqThresh::pktSize

[IN] Packet size (in 32-byte units) used in SOP FDQ selection

uint32_t CSL_UdmapRxFdqThresh::queue

[IN] Queue number to use if this threshold is selected
